

=Description=

"BlindBitCoin is a very clever bridge between electronic money (which is all about anonymous transactions) and bitcoin (which is a transparent p2p accounting and transfer system for units of 'digital gold' ). You can exchange bitcoins at BlindBitCoin into blinded electronic cash, using a javascript client that runs in the browser. You will get a long url which you can send to somebody, who can then redeem the coins (using the javascript client again)."
(http://opencoin.org/workspace/other-projects)


